{"type": "article", "id": 4843, "title": "Radius x Medicom Toy 联名耳机", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-31T08:32:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233752BVxhDlFw1r2Wj9ni.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t日本玩具厂商 Medicom Toy 日前联手手机配件制造商 Radius ，推出了一系列 Be@rbrick 联名耳机，在设计上选用了 Medicom Toy 招牌式的 Be@rbrick 小熊元素，将可爱的熊头与耳机听筒相结合，并赋予耳机各种明丽的配色，使得这一系列的产品充满了童真趣味。定价 2000 日元（约合人民币 104 元），预计将于 2015 年 1 月在<a href=\"http://item.rakuten.co.jp/project1-6/4530956469621/\" target=\"_blank\">日本乐天市场</a>、<a href=\"http://store.shopping.yahoo.co.jp/project1-6/beainnerear.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅虎日本</a>以及 <a href=\"http://cjmart.jp/products/detail.php?product_id=1426\" target=\"_blank\">C.J.MART</a> 3 大线上购物网站发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052337512uJp4HPE56VrfN3z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233751yl6c9JVOpU8I4DkK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233752wPJAFa9RyDUisNrY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}